{"tid":1071294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［之父］張超雄：我哋邊個祖宗唔係移民？","createTime":"2019-03-21T08:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T11:46:39.000Z","uid":49388,"like":3,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"49c0c216c5f92bca1bedf87d802a81eb1666dd5d","tid":1071294,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:55:37.000Z","msg":"工黨議員張超雄則替新移民辯護，不滿有人嘲諷內地新移民為「蝗蟲」，掠奪港人資源，「呢個係明顯嘅歧視，我哋邊個祖宗唔係移民？」他又指，新移民多是弱勢、基層婦女，而這班人也是港人的家人，跨境婚姻也是以基層為主，而且新移民來港後，當中不少人擔任照顧者的角色：「嚟港控制、威脅我哋嘅政治、文化，並唔係呢批人。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190321/59393431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190321%2F59393431&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3CZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=cf1622a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190321%2F59393431&h=e560bf87\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190321/59393431</a>"},{"pid":"fa3eec8da4c1c9981e240dc48b77cb88ff62c0f5","tid":1071294,"uid":182556,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:57:04.000Z","msg":"咁你快啲移民去陰間同你啲祖宗團聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32cc9dd86324924a1e4e6c14e1ddc28989afe52","tid":1071294,"uid":62822,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:57:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb0cbd8638e6e01fda4c07294d5781989229907e","tid":1071294,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:58:50.000Z","msg":"但投票比奶共兇手就正正係呢班陷家剷呢"},{"pid":"b46e5f92818e2aa0d0321fbe02fe3459386af124","tid":1071294,"uid":170383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:59:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"80076494bfd5c7d3338508a9a7864290a92d